YAGAJOBS,is,an,online,UK,jobs,service,that,provides,access,to,a,database,of,live,job,vacancies,gathered,from,numerous,UK,job,boards,YAGAJOBS,offers,a,normalized,and,constantly,refreshed,service,in,a,single,highly,comprehensive,database,The,YAGAJOBS,REST,API,searches,and,matches,vacancies,based,on,given,criteria,Data,attributes,are,normalized,and,include,advertiser,salary,location,title,description,type,hours,and,more,Supported,formats,include,simple,JSON,simple,XML,and,HR,XML,An,API,key,is,required